<HEADLINE>
<P>
OUTREACH TO RUSSIA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * As part of the United States' outreach to the new Russia, President Clinton 
should expand the mission of the Peace Corps, recruit the patriotic Ross Perot, 
and offer him as a political consultant to Vladimir Zhirinovsky. 
</P>
<P>
 E. P. MACUS 
</P>
<P>
 South Pasadena 
</P>
