</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Kate Foster 
</P>
<P>
 Sunny Hills, Jr. 
</P>
<P>
 Soccer / Forward 
</P>
<P>
 Foster, a defender last season and during summer league, was expected to 
continue in that role this season.But when Sunny Hills' coaches decided the 
Lancers needed help on offense, Foster was happy to step up. Last week, she had 
two goals and an assist in each of two Freeway League victories. Foster, who 
has six goals and three assists this season, accounted for all of the Lancers' 
goals in a 3-1 victory over La Habra, considered the most serious challenger to 
Sunny Hills' three-season hold on the league title. The Lancers also beat 
Sonora, 7-1. Other notables: 
